-dress-nice-perfume\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Jumu&#8217;ah: Friday is an Eid, dress nice, wear perfume","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has made\u00a0this day of Friday a celebration\u00a0for the Muslims. Whoever comes to Friday prayer, let him bathe himself, apply perfume if he has it, and use the toothstick.\u201d Source: Sunan\u00a0Ibn Ma\u0304jah 1098 Grade: Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/prophet-siwak-wake-up\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Miswak: The Prophet cleans his teeth after waking","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, arose at night, he would clean his mouth with the toothstick. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 243, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 255 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064f \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33110,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/prophet-siwak-often\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: The Prophet uses the toothstick often","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI was ordered to use the toothstick so often that I thought something of it would be sent down to me in the Quran or revealed to me.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2998 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5858,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/02\/siwak-miswak-before-salat-wudu\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Using a toothstick before prayer, ablution","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWere it not a burden upon my nation, I would have ordered them to use the toothstick before every prayer.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"I would have ordered them to use the toothstick with\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33104,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/clean-mouth-teeth-pleasing\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Siwak: Clean mouth and teeth pleasing to the Lord","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must use the toothstick, as it is pleasant for the mouth and pleasing to the Lord.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 5865 Source: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/05\/visit-prophet-bad-oral-hygiene\/","url_meta":{"origin":33108,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Teeth: You visit the Prophet with bad oral hygiene?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-\u2018Abbas reported: They entered upon the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, without having brushed their teeth. The Prophet said, \u201cYou enter upon me with unclean teeth? Go use the toothstick. Were it not hardship for my nation, I would have obligated them to use the toothstick\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33108","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33108"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33108\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33108"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=33108"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=33108"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}